name: Kirlia
description:
The last of my old LoRAs I will be uploading for now. This one is the oldest of the bunch and therefore the most finicky.

IMPORTANT:
To actually prompt Kirlia you should include most if not all of the required tags which I will reiterate here: kirlia, green hair, red eyes, white dress, green skin

Trained on Anything v3 and the demo images are from Anything v4.5 with a 0.8 LoRA weight
